<h2 id="why-both-stem-and-non-stem-phds-can-succeed-in-data-science">Why both STEM and non STEM PhDs can succeed in Data Science</h2>
<p>he basic assumptions that hold true for being a successful PhD are the same in Data Science. For me, the Data Science process is like the process I was doing while in Grad school:</p>

